# Cloudflare Pages — optional same-origin API proxy.
#
# By default we use a split-subdomain setup:
#    yexcel.hackknow.com       → Cloudflare Pages (this build)
#    api.yexcel.hackknow.com   → Fly.io backend
# The frontend reads NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL at build time and calls the backend
# directly, so no proxy is needed.
#
# If you'd rather serve everything from a single origin (e.g. you don't want
# to add a second CNAME), uncomment the lines below — Cloudflare will
# transparently proxy /api/* and /files/* to your Fly backend.
#
# /api/*    https://yai-excel-api.fly.dev/api/:splat    200
# /files/*  https://yai-excel-api.fly.dev/files/:splat  200
#
# SPA fallback — every unknown route renders the 404 page.
/*  /404.html  404
